$ torchrun --nproc_per_node=2 code/sp_demo.py --mode ring_attention
============================================================
Ring Attention Demo (Context Parallelism)
============================================================

World size: 2

Each GPU holds:
  Q: (1, 8, 4096, 64)
  K: (1, 8, 4096, 64)
  V: (1, 8, 4096, 64)

Total sequence length: 8192

------------------------------------------------------------
Ring Attention Steps:
------------------------------------------------------------
  Step 0: GPU 0 attends to KV from GPU 0
  Step 1: GPU 0 attends to KV from GPU 1
------------------------------------------------------------

After 2 steps:
  - Every Q has attended to all 8192 tokens
  - No GPU ever held the full 8192-token KV
  - Memory per GPU: 2x reduction vs full attention

